claim.claim-text:
1. A tack cart for storing and transporting tack, the cart including a frame that may be mounted on an independent support separated from the cart; the tack cart comprising: 
a base; 
a first frame connected to the base; 
a second frame connected to the first frame; the second frame being removable from the first frame and adapted to be mounted on the independent support.

15. A tack cart for transporting tack and including a member for storing tack on a support remote from the tack cart, the tack cart comprising; 
a conveying section having at least one wheel; 
a storage section attached to the conveying section, the storage section being detachable from the conveying section and being adapted to releasingly engage the support.

21. A tack cart for storing and transporting tack, the cart including a frame that may be mounted on an independent support separated from the cart; the tack cart comprising: (a) a base having mounted thereon: at least one wheel, and a ground-engaging support, said support being mounted a spaced distance from the wheel;
(b) a first frame connected to the base, said first frame having: two first side bars, two first end bars connected to the first side bars; and at least one first rib extending between the first side bars;
(c) a second frame connected to the first frame, said second frame having: two second side bars, two second end bars connected to the second side bars; and at least one second rib extending between the second side bars; said second frame being removable from the first frame and mountable on the independent support;
(d) at least one saddle support detachably mountable on one of the first rib and the second rib.
